The paper discusses the use of agile software development methods in the embedded domain, which involves hardware constraints. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) or Embedded Systems (cs.EM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the development of low-level telecommunications software, which could fall under the Programming Languages (cs.PL) or Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Finally, the paper is focused on the development process itself, which could also place it in the Software Development (cs.SD) sub-category.
